Java is an object - oriented programming language since it supports 6 main features that every OOPs languages should support. Java is class based programming language since 
in java everything is written inside of a class.

Features of OOPs : 1) Object
                   2) Class
                   3) Inheritance
                   4) Polymorphism
                   5) Encapsulation
                   6) Abstraction
                   
